name: Master Dreams
description: Cybernetic machines are not merely created in the written codes and programs inside a hackerâ€™s mind or his computer, but they need to be translated into practical machinations that wreak havoc in the corporate offices that are controlling our society. You are the master hands that stand behind the realization of the dreams of a revolution, the fuel of the years of oppression that have haunted humans and their freedom into a secluded corner. You are to devise, design, and build the metallic contraptions that would strive to destroy the corporate hegemony over society, and restore peace and freedom for all of us.
